Recommends: nginx | apache2 | httpd
Suggests: logrotate
Description: Dynamic gallery server with image resizing and templating
 DynServer is a high-performance web server designed for photo galleries
 with dynamic image resizing, template-based rendering, and secure download
 management. It features:
 .
  * Automatic image resizing and caching
  * Liquid templating engine for customizable layouts
  * EXIF data extraction and display
  * Masonry-style gallery layouts
  * Mobile-responsive design
  * Secure download authentication with signed cookies
  * Background cache management
 .
 This package includes the server binary, systemd service, example
 configuration, and default templates and static assets.